 I illustrate the ideas presented here by proposing a\nrenormalization group scheme for causal dynamical triangulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Sep 2014 20:00:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 2 Oct 2014 19:54:12 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 21 Oct 2014 13:19:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-10-22"}
