\ndetector in the presence of high-rate backgrounds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Sep 2014 23:56:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 7 Dec 2014 21:02:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-12-09"}
